highlights.text: “CLIMA LINDO - SLOWED” by GXMZ and Repsaj is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs South Korea, up 33 spots at #49.
“PASSO BEM SOLTO - Slowed” by ATLXS has been on Viral Songs South Korea the longest, at 153 days straight.
LEE CHANHYUK has the most spots on Viral Songs South Korea. “Endangered Love” is the highest at #1.
